Package GIS

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    box
    This class represents a box that used as an obstacle in the game each box has start point and end that represent it and unique id.
    fruit
    this class represent Fruit object each of fruit has : id,position and weight associated with him
    game
    This class represents game that contains Fruits, Packmans ghost and obstacles each of them has position and meta data associated with them, the game also include general score according to the Weight of the eaten fruits and the start time
    ghost
    this class represents the ghost element in the game
    metaDataFruit
    this class contains all the data of Fruit
    metaDataPack
    this class contains all the data of Packman
    packman
    this class represent Packman object each of packman has : id,position,speed,eating radius, ArrayList of fruits that he ate and more data associated with him
